### Portfolio CMS API Test Dosyası

### 1. Tüm portfolio verilerini getir
GET https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio
Accept: application/json

### 2. Kişisel bilgileri güncelle
PUT https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio/personal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Enes Gedik",
  "title": "Frontend Developer",
  "profileImage": "/images/profile.jpg",
  "cvDownloadLink": "/files/cv.pdf",
  "welcomeMessage": "Merhaba! Ben Enes, passionate bir frontend geliştiricisiyim."
}

### 3. Hakkımda bölümünü güncelle
PUT https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio/about
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "3+ yıllık deneyime sahip frontend developer. Modern web teknolojileri ile kullanıcı dostu arayüzler geliştiriyorum.",
  "skills": ["React", "JavaScript", "TypeScript", "Next.js", "CSS", "SCSS"],
  "yearsExperience": 3,
  "projectsCompleted": 15
}

### 4. Yeni proje ekle
POST https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Portfolio CMS",
  "description": "Next.js ve C# ile geliştirilmiş modern portfolio yönetim sistemi",
  "imageUrl": "/images/portfolio-cms.jpg",
  "projectUrl": "https://portfolio-cms.demo.com",
  "githubUrl": "https://github.com/user/portfolio-cms",
  "technologies": ["Next.js", "C#", "JSON", "SCSS"],
  "isActive": true
}

### 5. Projeleri listele
GET https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio/projects
Accept: application/json

### 6. Proje güncelle (ID: 1)
PUT https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio/projects/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "E-Ticaret Platformu (Güncellenmiş)",
  "description": "Responsive ve modern tasarıma sahip e-ticaret uygulaması",
  "imageUrl": "/images/ecommerce-updated.jpg",
  "projectUrl": "https://ecommerce.demo.com",
  "githubUrl": "https://github.com/user/ecommerce",
  "technologies": ["React", "Node.js", "MongoDB", "Stripe"],
  "isActive": true
}

### 7. Tema ayarlarını güncelle
PUT https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio/theme
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "primaryColor": "#2563eb",
  "secondaryColor": "#64748b",
  "backgroundColor": "#f8fafc",
  "textColor": "#1e293b",
  "fontFamily": "Inter, system-ui, sans-serif",
  "darkMode": false
}

### 8. Tema ayarlarını getir
GET https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio/theme
Accept: application/json

### 9. İletişim bilgilerini güncelle
PUT https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "enes@example.com",
  "phone": "+90 555 123 45 67",
  "location": "İstanbul, Türkiye",
  "social": {
    "linkedin": "linkedin.com/in/enesgedik",
    "github": "github.com/enesgedik",
    "twitter": "twitter.com/enesgedik",
    "instagram": "instagram.com/enesgedik",
    "website": "https://enesgedik.dev"
  }
}

### 10. Proje sil (ID: 1)
DELETE https://localhost:7155/api/portfolio/projects/1
Accept: application/json 